Create a new Anaconda Environment for the analysis project, running the code below in cmd;
          conda create --name cryptocurrency_analysis python=3
To activate the environment run in cmd;
          activate cryptocurerncy-analysis 
To install the following required dependencies in your environment run in cmd;
          conda install numpy pandas nb_conda jupyter plotly quandl
To start a notebook run in cmd;
          jupyter notebook
The following link will open your jupyter interactive notebook in your browser of choice
          http://localhost:8888/
Using the Kernel that was previously set up at
          Python [conda env:cryptocurrency-analysis]
import your dependencies of choice in the first code cell
          import os
          import numpy as np
          import pandas as pd
          import pickle
          import quandl
          from datetime import datetime
To enable offline access and use 
          import plotly.offline as py
          import plotly.graph_objs as go
          import plotly.figure_factory as ff
          py.init_notebook_mode(connected=True)
